listing.description:
No. 9 GARDINER PLACE, CITY CENTRE, Dublin 1

VIEWING Tomorrow Thursday 12th Nov 5.30pm to 6.30pm
A lovely Hall Floor one bed room unit in a lovely well maintained quiet period house in the centre of Dublin City.
(only 2 minute walk to O’Connell St.)
Located between Mountjoy Square and Parnell Square.
The accomodation is in good condition  and has an entrance hall.There accomodation has a  a screened bedroom with double bed and living room/kitchen. Seperate bathroom in the apartment. The Bathroom has W/C and shower. 
Electric heating with Night saver cheap electricity. The laundry facility in the house is shared.
Waste charges are included in rent
Rent €1195 p.m.  
Email Ken if interested
